originalText.text: This was the worst dentist experience I've ever had. I went in for a simple cleaning and she barely cleaned anything. She forgotten my entire right side and i kept asking her if she's sure she's done. The office itself is not very clean either. I would recommend people to never go here.

originalText.text: I have been going to Dr. Monica Cioroiu for at least 15 years. I would never dream of going to another dentist. She has been the best all around dentist I’ve ever gone to and I thank my lucky stars often, that I found a dentist who really cares and does everything she can to be of help!! I’d give her 100 stars if I could!!
